    "Html": "Here is a basic example:<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\">\r\n<p>DataGrid_Standard.Columns.Add(</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> { Header = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;First Name&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, Binding = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;FirstName&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> });<br>\r\nDataGrid_Standard.Columns.Add(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> { Header = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Last Name&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, Binding = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;LastName&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> });<br>\r\nDataGrid_Standard.Items.Add(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Person</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> { FirstName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;John&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, LastName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Smith&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> });<br>\r\nDataGrid_Standard.Items.Add(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Person</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> { FirstName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;John&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, LastName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Smith&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> });<br>\r\nDataGrid_Standard.Items.Add(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Person</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> { FirstName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;John&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, LastName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Smith&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> });<br>\r\nDataGrid_Standard.Items.Add(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Person</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> { FirstName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;John&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, LastName = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Smith&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> });\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
